After you was 14 you could go to a music hall, the first house, 'cos they used to have two houses a night, then. Go first house, be out by nine o'clock, or a quarter to nine. Be home by 9.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4947025 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9198485\charrsid5852327 Why couldn't you go before you were 14?
