\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7697837\charrsid5852327 nearby}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9198485\charrsid5852327 ? Did the families of those brothers live near you?
